Title: Lady Killer
Plot: As Allison teams up with Scanlon to track down the dangerous "cougar" they believe is responsible for the murders of young men, she also has visions that Devalos' campaign is in jeopardy, with someone plotting against him.
GuestStars: Brian Hallisay, Matthew Cohen, Jude Ciccolella, Sara Botsford, Edward Finlay, Peter Porte, Neil Schwary, Todd Weeks, Gina St. John, Mark Harelik, Rosanna Arquette
